	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam recte valeas; valde mihi est suspectum, quod nullas a te accipio literas, nec enim ita asuevi.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed forte destitueris argumento; verum concilium et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834" cert="high">Italia</placeName> abundans tibi suppeditaret.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Occasionem aliam itaque expecto.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In comitiis <placeName type="auto_name">Badenis</placeName> fuerunt iam dies multos legati; quid egerint, facile non dixero; scio <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l781" cert="high">Urianos</placeName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2450" cert="high">Suitenses</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2469" cert="high">Subsylvanos</placeName> reiecisse capita pacificationis et nova obtrudere, quae <placeName ref="l646" cert="high">Claronenses</placeName> repudiant.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Varius est rumor; sunt, qui affirment parare nescio quos quas turbas contra <placeName ref="l646" cert="high">Claronenses</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Hilfft dann wäder rächt noch guͤtikeit, so erbarms gott; der wölle allen geträngten zuͦ hilff kummen und den unlidigen übermuͦt demuͤtigen.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallia</placeName> nihil habemus, nisi quod confirmatur evangelii praedicationem perrumpere.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Deus det gratiam.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ich hab hütt brieff von <placeName ref="l1976" cert="high">Augspurg</placeName>, das <persName type="auto_name">Wilhelm von Gruntpach</persName> inn die acht gethan sampt sinem bystand, das er sich anhept stercken, die widerparth ouch.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">O miseram <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2498" cert="high">Germaniam</placeName> et multo miseriorem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862" cert="high">Helvetiam</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Miserere nostri domine et serva nos et ne tradideris confitentes nomen tuum in manus hostium verbi dei, ne tradideris nos alienis; tu nos castigato.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p4521" cert="high">Castellio</persName> <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basileae</placeName> mortuus est 29. decembris anni praeteriti.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vive et vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Oremus dominum, ut nos servet a malo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tiguri 21. ianuarii 1564.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saluta amicos etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullingerus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praestantissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8009" cert="high">Ioanni Fabritio</persName>, <placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Curiensis</placeName> ecclesiae fideli ministro, domino et fratri meo colendissimo et charissimo.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l98" cert="high">Chur</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
